The new stimulus bill includes churches and has implication for church staff.
It contains important information for you and your church about the CARES Act.
#2 Contact your local bank and let them know you want to participate in the Paycheck Protection Program from the CARES ActThis action is pretty straightforward.
After you find what your average monthly payroll costs are, multiply that number by 2.5.
